snippet.title: [Black Desert Mobile] Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BLACK DESERT MOBILE | A TRUE MMORPG AT YOUR FINGERTIPS

Tap into a world of epic battles and grand adventures, now available worldwide!
Join adventures from all around the world and discover a true mobile MMORPG.

*Black Desert Mobile - Download now!
